  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Independent Third Party Monitoring to support and maximise UK aid delivery in North East Nigeria</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">IMPACT Initiatives, with operational support from its global partner ACTED, in Consortium with Ground Truth Solutions as a sub-contracted partner, propose to conduct a Third Party Monitoring of the DFID-funded North East Nigeria Transition to Development (NENTAD) programme to provide an objective, external verification of aid delivery and ensured clear monitoring, accountability and analysis of good practices</narrative>
  </description>
